{"id":576573,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/01/【立此存照】颂歌新赛季•演艺篇（二）习主席来/","date":"2018-01-16T22:18:12Z","modified":"2018-01-16T22:18:12Z","title":"【立此存照】颂歌新赛季•演艺篇（二）习主席来到咱村里","content":"<section>\n<blockquote><p>“呀呀呀几多欢喜，习主席来了咱们村里；房子里面发光咧，呀呀呀谢谢您，问寒又问暖好仔细，就像邻居暖心底……”今日，由中国人民解放军空政文工团青年歌唱家刘一祯与男高音歌唱家王宏伟演唱的新歌<strong>《习主席来到咱村里》</strong>正式上线。歌曲表达了对国家精准扶贫政策带领百姓脱贫致富迈向全面小康的赞美，被誉为“<strong>精准扶贫时代赞</strong><strong>歌</strong>”。</p></blockquote>\n<section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\"></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p><span class=\"js_audio_frame db\"><span id=\"voice_main_MzIyNTgxMTc4OF8yMjQ3NDg4MjUy_0\" class=\"share_audio_context flex_context pages_reset\"><span id=\"voice_play_MzIyNTgxMTc4OF8yMjQ3NDg4MjUy_0\" class=\"db share_audio_switch\"></span><span id=\"voice_detail_MzIyNTgxMTc4OF8yMjQ3NDg4MjUy_0\" class=\"share_audio_info flex_bd db\"><strong id=\"voice_title_MzIyNTgxMTc4OF8yMjQ3NDg4MjUy_0\" class=\"share_audio_title\" role=\"link\">习主席来到咱村里</strong><span id=\"voice_author_MzIyNTgxMTc4OF8yMjQ3NDg4MjUy_0\" class=\"share_audio_tips db\"></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section class=\"\">作词：武海燕作曲：刘一祯</p>\n<p>配器：郝松</p>\n<p>演唱：刘一祯 王宏伟</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>呀呀呀呀呀呀</p>\n<p>呀呀呀快快起</p>\n<p>喜雀子叫得喳喳地</p>\n<p>村长说有人要来咧</p>\n<p>呀呀呀嚓嚓地</p>\n<p>小米汤熬得黄楞楞地</p>\n<p>不知道谁们要来咧</p>\n<p>呀呀呀呀呀呀</p>\n<p>咱到那村口看看去</p>\n<p>夹阵阵看看没人影</p>\n<p>见苗苗见不到心坎里</p>\n<p>左等等右等等还不见咧</p>\n<p>原来是起的太早咧</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>大红公鸡喔喔啼</p>\n<p>大花花母鸡咯咯蛋叫</p>\n<p>远远地听见汽车响</p>\n<p>转过了山路几道道弯</p>\n<p>绕过了圪梁梁走进了村</p>\n<p>听见一阵阵脚步声</p>\n<p>走到咱家里认认门</p>\n<p>哎呀呀</p>\n<p>远看近看就是您</p>\n<p>您是咱敬爱的习主席</p>\n<p>我在电视里见过您</p>\n<p>您和电视上一样样地</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>呀呀呀几多欢喜</p>\n<p>习主席来了咱们村里</p>\n<p>房子里面发光咧</p>\n<p>呀呀呀谢谢您</p>\n<p>问寒又问暖好仔细</p>\n<p>就像邻居暖心底</p>\n<p>呀呀呀呀呀呀</p>\n<p>老百姓生活您操心咧</p>\n<p>咱这里地脊薄收入低</p>\n<p>您在过农村您知道的</p>\n<p>扶贫攻坚政策好咧</p>\n<p>村支书办法也想了不少咧</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>您说咱要多种树</p>\n<p>咱们一定好好种</p>\n<p>南山上种了种北山</p>\n<p>等树长高了您再来看</p>\n<p>李家的稻谷张家的米</p>\n<p>地里瞅庄稼脚裹满泥</p>\n<p>圪台看井水知温饱</p>\n<p>主席呀</p>\n<p>自从您来了咱们村里</p>\n<p>俺们去地里不等天明</p>\n<p>浑身上下使不完的劲</p>\n<p>想您时电视上看看您</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>千里的行程万里路</p>\n<p>咱们老百姓跟着您</p>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n<section>\n<section><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-576639\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYlXMYSlY9a02NIoicatYlY5cQKnKkBvVeDJozlftqN0EG9ciahpK22PBJg-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYlXMYSlY9a02NIoicatYlY5cQKnKkBvVeDJozlftqN0EG9ciahpK22PBJg-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYlXMYSlY9a02NIoicatYlY5cQKnKkBvVeDJozlftqN0EG9ciahpK22PBJg-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYlXMYSlY9a02NIoicatYlY5cQKnKkBvVeDJozlftqN0EG9ciahpK22PBJg-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYlXMYSlY9a02NIoicatYlY5cQKnKkBvVeDJozlftqN0EG9ciahpK22PBJg.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>《习主席来到咱村里》以通俗、接地气的语言描绘出老百姓对习主席来到村里的盼望和喜悦，配上活泼、欢快、朗朗上口的旋律，充满浓郁的民族特色。歌唱家刘一祯与王宏伟高亢的歌声，赋予作品灵动、跳跃的时代感，唱出老百姓对于习主席的热爱和拥护，<strong>表达了人民群众在党的带领下打赢脱贫攻坚战，共同奔向全面小康的美好生活</strong>。</p>\n<p>《习主席来到咱村里》由<strong>武海燕作词，刘一祯作曲</strong>，充分展现出刘一祯的创作才华。她表示，每次看到一个个脱贫致富的暖心故事，都会被感动。刘一祯在基层演出的时候，恰逢当地脐橙喜获丰收，果农们为销路发愁。了解到情况后，刘一祯和果农们一起研究销路，卖出上万斤脐橙。作为一名党员，刘一祯深知消除贫困、改善民生，打赢脱贫攻坚战，逐步实现共同富裕十分迫切。刘一祯一方面积极践行党员职责，参与脱贫的实践中；另一方面潜心创作，以优秀的文艺作品为精准脱贫助力。于是，创作出这首歌颂共产党带领全国人民精准扶贫的时代赞歌。</p>\n<p>刘一祯不仅是优秀的青年歌唱家，还是“<strong>中国孝亲敬老楷模</strong>”、“<strong>全囯道德模范</strong>”、“<strong>全军先进老干部工作者</strong>”、“<strong>中囯敬老宣传员</strong>”。在她的艺术道路上，以“祯”情传递爱心，用行动履行责任。</p>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-576638\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYl5ZFiazUmxhsmQkGgPrIorBaGV2zbxvib0UlGa6CFggZH436wKm1AZw0w-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"357\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYl5ZFiazUmxhsmQkGgPrIorBaGV2zbxvib0UlGa6CFggZH436wKm1AZw0w-300x195.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYl5ZFiazUmxhsmQkGgPrIorBaGV2zbxvib0UlGa6CFggZH436wKm1AZw0w-768x498.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYl5ZFiazUmxhsmQkGgPrIorBaGV2zbxvib0UlGa6CFggZH436wKm1AZw0w-1024x664.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYl5ZFiazUmxhsmQkGgPrIorBaGV2zbxvib0UlGa6CFggZH436wKm1AZw0w-230x150.jpg 230w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYl5ZFiazUmxhsmQkGgPrIorBaGV2zbxvib0UlGa6CFggZH436wKm1AZw0w.jpg 1233w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></section>\n<section></section>\n<section class=\"\"><strong>王宏伟</strong>中央军委政治工作部歌舞团<strong>男高音歌唱家</strong>，<strong>国家一级演员</strong>，享受国务院“<strong>特殊政府津贴</strong>”。第九届、第十届全国青联常委，中国文艺志愿者协会理事，曾获得中央电视台“第九届全国青年歌手电视大奖赛”专业组民族唱法金奖、第八届“<strong>五个一工程奖</strong>”等奖项。</p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-576640\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYliaiblJE2LkQAwntgw5aYyadr73KEH4EXCqcGusgIQdZCiayUHJZHpEkng-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYliaiblJE2LkQAwntgw5aYyadr73KEH4EXCqcGusgIQdZCiayUHJZHpEkng-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYliaiblJE2LkQAwntgw5aYyadr73KEH4EXCqcGusgIQdZCiayUHJZHpEkng-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYliaiblJE2LkQAwntgw5aYyadr73KEH4EXCqcGusgIQdZCiayUHJZHpEkng-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/ssSnG9pG7k2oeSjz2NZsrZxsxbgGUsYliaiblJE2LkQAwntgw5aYyadr73KEH4EXCqcGusgIQdZCiayUHJZHpEkng.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></section>\n<section></section>\n<section class=\"\"><strong>刘一祯</strong>中国人民解放军空军政治工作部文工团<strong>著名青年歌唱家</strong>，全国青联委员，北京市第十五届人大代表，中国文联文艺志愿者；先后毕业于湖南师范大学音乐系（本科）、原解放军艺术学院音乐系（硕士）、湖南师范大学音乐系（博士）。曾先后获得<strong>全军文艺会演演唱一等奖</strong>、<strong>全军文艺会演戏剧表演一等奖</strong>、<strong>中国金唱片奖</strong>、环球旅游音乐榜年度“<strong>十大金曲奖</strong>”等奖项。</p>\n</section>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>中国数字空间︱<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%B4%87%E6%8B%9C\">习近平个人崇拜</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>【<a class=\"st_tag internal_tag\" title=\"Posts tagged with 立此存照\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7/\" rel=\"tag\">立此存照</a>】<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%AD%A4%E5%AD%98%E7%85%A7%E3%80%91%E9%A2%82%E6%AD%8C%E6%96%B0%E8%B5%9B%E5%AD%A3%E2%80%A2%E8%87%AA%E5%97%A8%E7%AF%87%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%EF%BC%9A/\">颂歌新赛季•自嗨篇（一）习近平：新时代的领路人</a></p>\n<p>【立此存照】<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e9%a2%82%e6%ad%8c%e6%96%b0%e8%b5%9b%e5%ad%a3%e2%80%a2%e6%bc%94%e8%89%ba%e7%af%87%ef%bc%88%e4%b8%80%ef%bc%89%e4%b8%9c%e6%96%b9%e5%86%8d%e5%8d%87/\">颂歌新赛季•演